	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-08-20T07:37:01">Merlin Entertainments plc is a United Kingdom-based entertainments company. The Company operates around 105 attractions in 23 countries across four continents. The Company operates through three business segments: Midway Attractions, LEGOLAND Parks and Resort Theme Parks. The Midway Attractions are smaller, indoor attractions located in city centers or resorts. The Midway Attractions segment operates around 92 attractions in 21 countries across four continents. The LEGOLAND Parks includes LEGO themed accommodation, rides and shows. The LEGOLAND Parks segment operates around six attractions in five countries across three continents. The Resort Theme Parks includes accommodation, rides and shows. The Resort Theme Parks segment operates around six attractions in the United Kingdom, Germany and Italy.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2015-08-03T14:32:22">BRIEF: For the 26 weeks ended 27 June 2015, Merlin Entertainments PLC revenues increased 6% to L544M. Net income decreased 14% to L25M. Revenues reflect Midway Attractions segment increase of 8% to L252M, LEGOLAND Parks segment increase of 10% to L178M, Other items segment increase of 100% to L2M. Net income was offset by Resort Theme Parks segment loss increase of 67% to L20M, Other items segment loss increase of 6% to L18M.</Text>
	</TextInfo>
